description: Maanas is taking their renowned Indian cuisine on the move!Decadent dining has come to the streets of Columbus, so you can have all the best Indian eating you'll ever sink your teeth into. Whether you crave some Curry in a Hurry, a Classic Biryani, or some of their delicious Wraps, and Bowls, this truck is sure to satisfy.Find them out and about on the streets of Columbus, or catering the coolest events in your area, for an eating experience you'll never forget.
name: Maanas
